## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of publicly accessible information and the interpretations of the events by different sources. Some motivations behind the attacks may remain speculative due to the secretive nature of terrorist organizations and the lack of direct statements from the perpetrators. Additionally, the geopolitical context and the responses to the attacks have evolved over time, which may influence current interpretations of the events.